    @BaseClass
public class NeighborCF3d
extends net.hudup.core.alg.cf.NeighborCF2d
    This class sets up an advanced version of 3-dimensional neighbor collaborative filtering (Neighbor CF) algorithm. Note that similarity for this algorithm must be normalized in interval [0, 1].
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
